                  , thē did the Iſraelites well to crucifie Chriſt, becauſe the high Prieſtes and Elders conſented thereto. For it is al one to ſay, Aaron gaue his conſent to make the Iſraelites a Calfe, and therefore is Idolatrie good: as to ſay, the Churchwardens doe ſuffer men to daunce vpon the Sabboath day, therefore is dauncing lawfull vpon the Sabboath day.
            
            
               Iu.
