               Iu.
               Perhaps you ſayd truer there then you were aware off. But well I can not tell, there were neuer ſo many whoores and theeues as there haue beene ſince dauncinge was ſo muche left.
               For when as dauncinge was vſed, then men &amp; women came abrode, and now they creep into corners, either to filtch or els to play the naughtipackes.
            
            
               Min.
